libshapedraw.event

Class LSDGameTickEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • libshapedraw.event.LSDEvent
      • libshapedraw.event.LSDGameTickEvent

  • public class LSDGameTickEvent
extends LSDEvent
    Event fired once per game tick, occurring every 1/20th of a second. This happens less frequently than LSDPreRenderEvent. Exactly how much less depends on the end user's FPS.
